                        base="i1052997"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.223-3</xref>, Hazardous Material Identification and Material Safety Data, in solicitations and contracts if the contract will require the delivery of hazardous materials as defined in <xref href="FAR-i1094805.dita#i1094805"
